      "text": "BOATノート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866321,
      "updated": 1777866321
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816500000000000552b15",
      "text": " エバーグリーンノートになる前の状態のノート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866321,
      "updated": 1777866340
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b16",
      "text": " 完成度が低いノート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866340
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b17",
      "text": " 気楽にノートを作れるようにするための仕組み",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866340
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b18",
      "text": " まずは[小さく始める]、それを[少しずつ改善していく]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1780975804
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b19",
      "text": "  簡単なことを繰り返す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866340
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b1a",
      "text": "  シンプルな方法は決断疲れが起こりにくい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866340
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b1b",
      "text": " [BOAT note]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866373
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b1c",
      "text": " [BOAT] : [block of atomic thought]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866384
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b1d",
      "text": " [アトミックノート]（[atomic note]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866393
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b1e",
      "text": " [エバーグリーンノート]（[evergreen notes]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777866322,
      "updated": 1777866403
    },
    {
      "id": "69f816510000000000552b1f",
